get_openapi_spec
================

.. autofunction:: get_openapi_spec

Gets the OpenAPI spec for a plugin.

Parameters
----------
url : str
    The URL of the plugin.

Returns
-------
dict
    The OpenAPI spec for the plugin.

Purpose
-------
This function is used to retrieve the OpenAPI spec for a plugin given its URL. The OpenAPI spec describes the endpoints, parameters and responses of the API.


